♪We forever live for love's sake♪

20
00:01:23,565 --> 00:01:33,824
♪Shadow's spear burns fiercely♪

21
00:01:35,251 --> 00:01:40,800
=Legend of The Female General=

22
00:01:46,000 --> 00:01:48,912
=Episode 8=

23
00:01:52,880 --> 00:01:54,440
Thank you for coming all this way,

24
00:01:54,960 --> 00:01:56,160
Mr. Chu, to help us

25
00:01:56,440 --> 00:01:58,240
settle the issue

26
00:01:58,600 --> 00:02:00,000
with Yezhou Garrison.

27
00:02:00,752 --> 00:02:02,440
Please, have some tea.

28
00:02:03,319 --> 00:02:04,520
Don't mention it, Mr. Sun.

29
00:02:07,160 --> 00:02:08,919
How is the Chancellor?

30
00:02:09,440 --> 00:02:10,520
Master is fine,

31
00:02:11,240 --> 00:02:12,360
though somewhat troubled.

32
00:02:15,279 --> 00:02:16,159
Who dares to

33
00:02:16,399 --> 00:02:17,439
cause distress

34
00:02:17,559 --> 00:02:18,448
to the Chancellor?

35
00:02:22,599 --> 00:02:24,999
Could it be Xiao Jue?

36
00:02:30,640 --> 00:02:31,719
You're mistaken, Mr. Sun.

37
00:02:32,399 --> 00:02:33,719
What troubles the Chancellor

38
00:02:34,320 --> 00:02:35,719
is naturally the state affairs.

39
00:02:37,776 --> 00:02:38,640
Of course.

40
00:02:38,999 --> 00:02:39,839
Of course.

41
00:02:40,480 --> 00:02:42,040
I merely wish to share

42
00:02:42,192 --> 00:02:43,088
his burdens.

43
00:02:46,000 --> 00:02:46,928
Mr. Chu.

44
00:02:47,399 --> 00:02:49,719
You've traveled this great distance.

45
00:02:49,960 --> 00:02:51,559
I've prepared a welcoming banquet.

46
00:02:51,559 --> 00:02:52,400
I hope you will

47
00:02:52,400 --> 00:02:53,960
grace us with your presence.

48
00:02:56,559 --> 00:02:57,920
The guest of honor must be

49
00:02:58,599 --> 00:02:59,599
Commander Xiao, right?

50
00:03:01,760 --> 00:03:02,960
Speaking of Commander Xiao,

51
00:03:03,279 --> 00:03:04,119
I have

52
00:03:04,119 --> 00:03:06,159
so much to say.

53
00:03:06,599 --> 00:03:07,520
He's sent me missives

54
00:03:07,920 --> 00:03:09,399
since his appointment,

55
00:03:09,760 --> 00:03:10,679
demanding either funds

56
00:03:10,679 --> 00:03:11,520
or provisions.

57
00:03:11,920 --> 00:03:13,200
But we're having

58
00:03:13,520 --> 00:03:14,360
a difficult time

59
00:03:14,879 --> 00:03:16,159
in Yezhou.

60
00:03:17,760 --> 00:03:18,768
The Chancellor

61
00:03:19,040 --> 00:03:20,240
is fully aware

62
00:03:20,360 --> 00:03:21,559
of all the circumstances.

63
00:03:26,879 --> 00:03:29,159
What are you implying, Mr. Sun?

64
00:03:29,559 --> 00:03:30,920
Master resides in Yaojing.

65
00:03:31,879 --> 00:03:34,119
How could he know what's going on here?

66
00:03:37,200 --> 00:03:38,119
I misspoke.

67
00:03:38,679 --> 00:03:40,599
I apologize.

68
00:03:42,928 --> 00:03:43,824
Ding Yi.

69
00:03:44,112 --> 00:03:45,040
Come here.

70
00:03:45,879 --> 00:03:47,599
Meet Mr. Chu Zhao.

71
00:03:47,952 --> 00:03:48,912
Mr. Chu.

72
00:03:49,360 --> 00:03:50,559
This is Ding Yi.

73
00:03:50,920 --> 00:03:51,760
General Feihong

74
00:03:51,800 --> 00:03:52,960
sent him over.

75
00:03:53,584 --> 00:03:54,512
Greetings, Mr. Chu.

76
00:03:54,768 --> 00:03:55,632
General says

77
00:03:56,200 --> 00:03:57,159
I'm at your disposal

78
00:03:57,800 --> 00:03:59,200
whenever you need me.

79
00:04:00,679 --> 00:04:02,200
General Feihong is too kind.

80
00:04:02,608 --> 00:04:03,536
I don't need you

81
00:04:03,536 --> 00:04:04,400
for anything.

82
00:04:07,792 --> 00:04:08,719
Mr. Chu.

83
00:04:08,719 --> 00:04:09,719
Excuse me for a second.

84
00:04:09,960 --> 00:04:11,119
Let me check on

85
00:04:11,320 --> 00:04:12,279
the banquet.

86
00:04:12,559 --> 00:04:13,960
With two distinguished guests here,

87
00:04:14,119 --> 00:04:16,336
- I dare not make any mistakes.
- Indeed.

88
00:04:16,480 --> 00:04:17,599
Make thorough preparation.

89
00:04:18,192 --> 00:04:19,056
Master.

90
00:04:21,648 --> 00:04:22,352
Master.

91
00:04:22,479 --> 00:04:23,880
It's Commander Xiao and Mr. Cheng.

92
00:04:26,864 --> 00:04:27,600
Mr. Chu.

93
00:04:36,120 --> 00:04:37,320
(Sun Mansion)
What an honor, Commander.

94
00:04:37,359 --> 00:04:38,719
Forgive me for failing

95
00:04:38,719 --> 00:04:40,520
to greet you properly.

96
00:04:43,880 --> 00:04:45,039
Please meet the inspector,

97
00:04:45,039 --> 00:04:46,760
Mr. Chu Zhao.

98
00:04:47,880 --> 00:04:48,496
Commander Xiao.

99
00:04:48,719 --> 00:04:49,440
Long time no see.

100
00:04:49,760 --> 00:04:50,320
Mr. Chu.

101
00:04:51,000 --> 00:04:51,719
Long time no see.

102
00:04:57,200 --> 00:04:57,960
(It's him?)

103
00:04:58,919 --> 00:04:59,799
(Come to think of it,)

104
00:05:00,120 --> 00:05:01,760
(I once swindled him.)

105
00:05:02,239 --> 00:05:03,520
(But I did give him medicine.)

106
00:05:03,760 --> 00:05:04,799
(I guess we're even.)

107
00:05:05,520 --> 00:05:06,279
Nice to meet you.

108
00:05:06,919 --> 00:05:07,680
Mr. Cheng.

109
00:05:09,239 --> 00:05:10,039
(It looks like)

110
00:05:10,200 --> 00:05:11,520
(he's not going to expose me)

111
00:05:11,520 --> 00:05:12,479
(in public.)

112
00:05:15,239 --> 00:05:15,880
I am

113
00:05:16,752 --> 00:05:17,839
Cheng Lisu.

114
00:05:18,159 --> 00:05:19,039
Greetings, Inspector.

115
00:05:30,080 --> 00:05:30,880
What is it, Father?

116
00:05:30,880 --> 00:05:31,408
Ling.

117
00:05:31,560 --> 00:05:33,039
Apologize to Commander Xiao

118
00:05:33,080 --> 00:05:34,440
and Mr. Cheng.

119
00:05:40,440 --> 00:05:42,239
Sorry, I have offended you.

120
00:05:42,399 --> 00:05:43,200
Please kindly

121
00:05:43,960 --> 00:05:44,760
forgive me.

122
00:05:48,880 --> 00:05:49,599
Go on.

123
00:05:51,080 --> 00:05:52,159
I'm unworthy of your anger.

124
00:05:54,399 --> 00:05:56,479
So you realize that

125
00:05:56,599 --> 00:05:57,719
you're unworthy?

126
00:06:05,159 --> 00:06:06,719
Shall we be seated

127
00:06:07,080 --> 00:06:07,760
first?

128
00:06:08,200 --> 00:06:08,719
Commander.

129
00:06:09,359 --> 00:06:11,000
You need to talk to Mr. Sun.

130
00:06:11,320 --> 00:06:11,880
Go ahead.

131
00:06:25,760 --> 00:06:26,320
Please.

132
00:06:39,306 --> 00:06:42,288
(Peace and Harmony)

133
00:06:47,680 --> 00:06:48,359
Commander.

134
00:06:48,760 --> 00:06:49,719
You assumed

135
00:06:49,880 --> 00:06:51,159
your position some time ago.

136
00:06:51,399 --> 00:06:52,479
I haven't had the chance

137
00:06:52,599 --> 00:06:53,599
to pay my respects.

138
00:06:53,799 --> 00:06:54,640
Instead,

139
00:06:54,760 --> 00:06:56,000
you came to see me first.

140
00:06:56,120 --> 00:06:57,599
I feel so guilty.

141
00:06:58,440 --> 00:06:59,080
Let me

142
00:06:59,680 --> 00:07:00,640
toast to you.

143
00:07:01,719 --> 00:07:02,680
You're too kind.

144
00:07:04,279 --> 00:07:05,359
I don't mind visiting

145
00:07:05,399 --> 00:07:06,479
as long as we work out

146
00:07:06,839 --> 00:07:08,159
the problems of supplies

147
00:07:08,919 --> 00:07:09,640
and funds.

148
00:07:14,000 --> 00:07:15,320
Commander, your words

149
00:07:15,640 --> 00:07:17,919
make me burn with shame.

150
00:07:20,399 --> 00:07:22,080
An army without supplies perishes.

151
00:07:22,320 --> 00:07:22,960
That

152
00:07:23,359 --> 00:07:24,120
I know.

153
00:07:24,440 --> 00:07:25,880
I also want to handle it

154
00:07:25,960 --> 00:07:27,239
perfectly.

155
00:07:27,719 --> 00:07:28,320
It's just that

156
00:07:28,719 --> 00:07:30,039
our county granary has had

157
00:07:30,080 --> 00:07:31,640
no grain reserves for years.

158
00:07:32,039 --> 00:07:33,039
I truly can't

159
00:07:33,120 --> 00:07:34,520
raise any funds.

160
00:07:35,880 --> 00:07:37,399
Despite such hardships,

161
00:07:38,200 --> 00:07:39,320
you are still able

162
00:07:39,719 --> 00:07:40,719
to treat us to such

163
00:07:41,080 --> 00:07:42,120
lavish delicacies.

164
00:07:42,919 --> 00:07:43,640
Mr. Sun,

165
00:07:44,839 --> 00:07:45,599
you're too kind.

166
00:07:47,159 --> 00:07:48,200
Don't mention it.

167
00:07:49,440 --> 00:07:50,000
It's good

168
00:07:50,680 --> 00:07:52,359
that the inspector is also here.

169
00:07:53,000 --> 00:07:53,599
Mr. Chu,

170
00:07:54,279 --> 00:07:55,960
we should absolutely look into

171
00:07:56,799 --> 00:07:57,799
the tax ledger

172
00:07:58,719 --> 00:08:00,479
for the tax collection details.

173
00:08:01,239 --> 00:08:02,512
Was the tax left uncollected,

174
00:08:03,520 --> 00:08:05,120
or was there foul play?

175
00:08:12,080 --> 00:08:13,760
We're counting on you, Mr. Chu.

176
00:08:16,159 --> 00:08:16,680
Mr. Sun.

177
00:08:18,320 --> 00:08:18,919
I'm here.

178
00:08:19,279 --> 00:08:19,960
Shouldn't you

179
00:08:20,399 --> 00:08:21,719
toast Mr. Chu?

180
00:08:26,599 --> 00:08:28,159
A timely reminder, Commander.

181
00:08:28,440 --> 00:08:29,008
I was

182
00:08:29,399 --> 00:08:30,719
almost rude.

183
00:08:32,479 --> 00:08:33,000
Mr. Chu,

184
00:08:34,520 --> 00:08:35,599
here is to you.

185
00:08:35,799 --> 00:08:37,400
I beg your forgiveness.

186
00:08:40,160 --> 00:08:40,752
Ling.

187
00:08:43,599 --> 00:08:45,400
Please forgive me.

188
00:08:51,440 --> 00:08:52,400
Please don't say that.

189
00:08:52,680 --> 00:08:53,719
Duties take precedence.

190
00:08:54,280 --> 00:08:54,920
Besides,

191
00:08:55,359 --> 00:08:56,320
this concerns

192
00:08:56,639 --> 00:08:58,519
the basic welfare of the soldiers,

193
00:08:58,879 --> 00:08:59,960
which is the top priority.

194
00:09:00,440 --> 00:09:01,879
I will spare no effort

195
00:09:02,119 --> 00:09:03,879
in fulfilling my inspection duties.

196
00:09:04,599 --> 00:09:06,119
Thank you, Mr. Chu.

197
00:09:09,599 --> 00:09:10,560
We appreciate it.

198
00:09:15,320 --> 00:09:16,639
Enough of unpleasant talks.

199
00:09:17,400 --> 00:09:17,920
I will stay

200
00:09:18,359 --> 00:09:19,960
at your mansion for a few days.

201
00:09:20,320 --> 00:09:20,839
I hope

202
00:09:21,239 --> 00:09:22,839
I won't ruin your mood, Mr. Sun.

203
00:09:24,040 --> 00:09:24,960
Not at all.

204
00:09:25,680 --> 00:09:27,400
It's my honor

205
00:09:27,759 --> 00:09:29,920
to have you reside here.

206
00:09:32,800 --> 00:09:34,160
To complement this occasion,

207
00:09:34,519 --> 00:09:35,080
I have

208
00:09:35,239 --> 00:09:36,599
prepared a little show

209
00:09:36,879 --> 00:09:37,479
to enhance

210
00:09:37,639 --> 00:09:38,200
festivities.

211
00:09:53,034 --> 00:09:54,416
(Peace and Harmony)

212
00:09:56,599 --> 00:09:58,359
(That man visited the Wanhua Pavilion)

213
00:09:59,119 --> 00:10:00,440
(to select dancers.)

214
00:11:21,639 --> 00:11:22,200
Someone.

215
00:11:22,599 --> 00:11:24,759
Bring forth my aged vintage

216
00:11:24,759 --> 00:11:25,280
from storage.

217
00:11:25,560 --> 00:11:27,280
Let our guests sample it.

218
00:11:50,160 --> 00:11:50,800
Commander.

219
00:11:51,560 --> 00:11:52,200
Mr. Cheng.

220
00:11:52,719 --> 00:11:54,040
Let me toast you both.

221
00:11:54,680 --> 00:11:55,320
Bottoms up.

222
00:12:13,999 --> 00:12:14,759
Uncle, I toast you.

223
00:12:18,320 --> 00:12:18,960
Uncle.

224
00:12:19,239 --> 00:12:19,879
It's poisoned.

225
00:12:19,960 --> 00:12:21,040
This wine is poisoned.

226
00:12:24,656 --> 00:12:25,328
I...

227
00:12:25,560 --> 00:12:26,440
I had no idea.

228
00:12:27,519 --> 00:12:28,280
Guards.

229
00:12:32,080 --> 00:12:33,440
Oh my! Help!

230
00:12:33,560 --> 00:12:35,160
Oh my! Assassins!

231
00:12:35,999 --> 00:12:37,280
Assassins!

232
00:12:40,639 --> 00:12:41,200
Sun Xiangfu.

233
00:12:41,320 --> 00:12:42,400
Summon the guards.

234
00:12:42,920 --> 00:12:43,800
Guards.

235
00:12:44,280 --> 00:12:45,280
Guards.

236
00:12:45,719 --> 00:12:46,560
Didn't you hear us?

237
00:12:46,999 --> 00:12:47,759
Guards.

238
00:12:48,119 --> 00:12:49,119
Are you dead?

239
00:13:03,920 --> 00:13:04,479
Watch out.

240
00:13:17,400 --> 00:13:18,239
Help.

241
00:13:21,936 --> 00:13:22,839
Help me.

242
00:13:31,119 --> 00:13:31,759
Help.

243
00:13:53,280 --> 00:13:53,808
Uncle.

244
00:14:41,440 --> 00:14:42,200
Guards.

245
00:14:42,440 --> 00:14:43,519
Get the corpses out.

246
00:14:44,960 --> 00:14:45,680
Wait.

247
00:14:50,759 --> 00:14:51,359
Uncle.

248
00:14:54,519 --> 00:14:55,280
I think

249
00:14:55,519 --> 00:14:56,440
I've gone blind.

250
00:15:24,119 --> 00:15:25,160
Assassins

251
00:15:25,960 --> 00:15:27,040
and poisoned wine?

252
00:15:29,560 --> 00:15:31,040
Any explanations?

253
00:15:35,359 --> 00:15:35,888
Commander.

254
00:15:36,519 --> 00:15:38,352
I swear I have no idea

255
00:15:38,352 --> 00:15:39,999
what happened here.

256
00:15:40,759 --> 00:15:41,560
I know nothing

257
00:15:41,680 --> 00:15:42,680
about the poison, either.

258
00:15:46,759 --> 00:15:48,960
This happened in your mansion.

259
00:15:51,599 --> 00:15:52,920
But your people

260
00:15:52,920 --> 00:15:54,359
act completely innocent.

261
00:15:55,400 --> 00:15:56,560
Isn't it ridiculous?

262
00:16:00,400 --> 00:16:01,519
We don't know the dancers

263
00:16:01,759 --> 00:16:02,800
and musicians.

264
00:16:03,119 --> 00:16:04,119
They were hired.

265
00:16:08,759 --> 00:16:09,296
Kneel.

266
00:16:09,599 --> 00:16:10,280
- I...
- Kneel.

267
00:16:10,800 --> 00:16:11,359
Kneel.

268
00:16:11,999 --> 00:16:12,680
No matter what,

269
00:16:13,040 --> 00:16:15,320
as head of the Sun family,

270
00:16:15,759 --> 00:16:16,800
I failed to protect you

271
00:16:17,400 --> 00:16:18,680
due to my negligence

272
00:16:18,999 --> 00:16:20,440
and nearly caused a catastrophe.

273
00:16:20,719 --> 00:16:22,359
I await your punishment, Commander.

274
00:16:26,759 --> 00:16:28,239
Are you saying

275
00:16:28,839 --> 00:16:30,479
that we should let this matter drop?

276
00:16:30,960 --> 00:16:31,440
I dare not.

277
00:16:31,680 --> 00:16:33,999
I'll get to the bottom of this.

278
00:16:34,680 --> 00:16:36,519
All assassins took poison

279
00:16:37,080 --> 00:16:38,160
and dropped dead.

280
00:16:38,680 --> 00:16:39,800
I'm not leaving until

281
00:16:40,239 --> 00:16:41,080
I find the truth.

282
00:16:41,680 --> 00:16:42,800
I'll help you investigate,

283
00:16:43,359 --> 00:16:44,320
Mr. Sun.

284
00:16:47,560 --> 00:16:48,879
Commander Xiao is right.

285
00:16:49,719 --> 00:16:50,839
As a witness,

286
00:16:51,160 --> 00:16:51,999
I'm also obligated

287
00:16:52,359 --> 00:16:53,200
to uncover the truth

288
00:16:53,639 --> 00:16:54,759
and catch the culprit.

289
00:16:59,999 --> 00:17:01,160
I appreciate it, Inspector.

290
00:17:21,600 --> 00:17:22,440
How do you feel?

291
00:17:23,719 --> 00:17:24,759
It's hurting less.

292
00:17:25,680 --> 00:17:27,039
I'm just not used to it.

293
00:17:31,120 --> 00:17:31,640
Earlier,

294
00:17:32,200 --> 00:17:32,960
I requested

295
00:17:32,960 --> 00:17:34,039
some soothing cream.

296
00:17:34,880 --> 00:17:35,759
It should arrive soon.

297
00:17:37,799 --> 00:17:38,319
Commander.

298
00:17:38,719 --> 00:17:39,680
Don't worry about me.

299
00:17:46,960 --> 00:17:47,559
Xiao Jue.

300
00:17:48,680 --> 00:17:50,360
Are you feeling sorry for me?

301
00:17:54,279 --> 00:17:55,519
Maybe you even feel guilty.

302
00:17:56,079 --> 00:17:57,079
But actually,

303
00:17:57,559 --> 00:17:58,600
you should praise me.

304
00:17:59,880 --> 00:18:00,640
For what?

305
00:18:01,680 --> 00:18:03,120
For being remarkable, obviously.

306
00:18:03,759 --> 00:18:04,440
If I hadn't

307
00:18:04,519 --> 00:18:05,880
stopped you from having the wine,

308
00:18:06,160 --> 00:18:07,400
you'd be dead now.

309
00:18:07,880 --> 00:18:09,440
I'm basically your lifesaver.

310
00:18:09,799 --> 00:18:10,840
Isn't that impressive?

311
00:18:14,519 --> 00:18:15,799
You don't seem distressed

312
00:18:17,120 --> 00:18:18,400
about losing your sight.

313
00:18:19,799 --> 00:18:21,880
Possibly forever.

314
00:18:31,039 --> 00:18:31,920
(She's scared.)

315
00:18:33,600 --> 00:18:34,759
(She's not as casual)

316
00:18:34,759 --> 00:18:35,559
(as she appears.)

317
00:18:38,519 --> 00:18:39,824
The blind aren't all the same.

318
00:18:40,559 --> 00:18:41,640
With my capabilities,

319
00:18:42,920 --> 00:18:43,960
I'll surely become

320
00:18:44,360 --> 00:18:44,920
the most

321
00:18:44,920 --> 00:18:46,039
formidable blind person.

322
00:18:54,079 --> 00:18:54,840
What

323
00:18:55,640 --> 00:18:57,160
happened tonight?

324
00:18:58,920 --> 00:18:59,759
Did you

325
00:18:59,759 --> 00:19:00,960
plot all this?

326
00:19:07,760 --> 00:19:08,440
Well...

327
00:19:09,079 --> 00:19:11,120
How can you be such a fool?

328
00:19:12,120 --> 00:19:12,759
And you.

329
00:19:15,440 --> 00:19:16,960
How dare you act so recklessly?

330
00:19:17,759 --> 00:19:18,400
What should I

331
00:19:18,440 --> 00:19:19,479
tell General Feihong?

332
00:19:22,640 --> 00:19:23,239
Unless

333
00:19:24,880 --> 00:19:26,719
he sent you here exactly for this.

334
00:19:32,640 --> 00:19:33,719
Please, Mr. Chu.

335
00:19:34,279 --> 00:19:35,759
Though we acted on our own,

336
00:19:36,039 --> 00:19:36,799
it was solely

337
00:19:36,799 --> 00:19:38,160
for the Chancellor's sake.

338
00:19:38,832 --> 00:19:39,408
You see.

339
00:19:39,680 --> 00:19:40,680
Everyone here knows

340
00:19:40,799 --> 00:19:42,039
that I work for the Chancellor.

341
00:19:42,239 --> 00:19:42,999
Xiao Jue came

342
00:19:43,079 --> 00:19:44,039
and humiliated me.

343
00:19:44,319 --> 00:19:45,440
He's not coming after me.

344
00:19:45,600 --> 00:19:46,759
He's after Mr. Xu!

345
00:19:46,759 --> 00:19:47,360
Mr. Sun.

346
00:19:53,440 --> 00:19:55,160
Your arrogance astounds me.

347
00:19:56,120 --> 00:19:57,039
Yezhou barely contains

348
00:19:57,079 --> 00:19:58,079
your inflated ego.

349
00:20:03,279 --> 00:20:04,680
Please forgive me.

350
00:20:09,999 --> 00:20:11,239
I don't care

351
00:20:11,920 --> 00:20:13,079
what you do.

352
00:20:13,799 --> 00:20:14,352
Anyway,

353
00:20:15,120 --> 00:20:16,880
if Master's reputation suffers damage,

354
00:20:17,239 --> 00:20:18,200
both you and I

355
00:20:18,920 --> 00:20:20,039
will be held accountable.

356
00:20:20,799 --> 00:20:21,479
It won't happen.

357
00:20:24,039 --> 00:20:24,640
Rest assured.

358
00:20:24,960 --> 00:20:25,719
Xiao Jue will not

359
00:20:25,799 --> 00:20:27,200
leave Yezhou alive.

360
00:20:27,600 --> 00:20:28,960
I dare not cause the Chancellor

361
00:20:29,039 --> 00:20:30,079
any trouble.

362
00:20:30,759 --> 00:20:32,360
I will make sure there are

363
00:20:33,440 --> 00:20:34,360
no loose ends.

364
00:20:41,079 --> 00:20:41,999
Take care, Mr. Chu.

365
00:20:55,360 --> 00:20:56,200
We underestimated

366
00:20:56,319 --> 00:20:57,960
Xiao Jue's martial prowess.

367
00:20:58,640 --> 00:21:00,319
And that Cheng Lisu...

368
00:21:01,279 --> 00:21:02,719
He spilled the wine

369
00:21:03,319 --> 00:21:05,239
way too conveniently.

370
00:21:07,360 --> 00:21:08,880
I think I have

371
00:21:10,960 --> 00:21:12,719
seen him somewhere.

372
00:21:20,680 --> 00:21:21,319
Commander.

373
00:21:22,239 --> 00:21:23,279
Won't you look into

374
00:21:23,559 --> 00:21:24,840
the assassination?

375
00:21:25,759 --> 00:21:26,559
How did assassins

376
00:21:26,880 --> 00:21:28,319
infiltrate the Sun Mansion?

377
00:21:28,600 --> 00:21:30,759
Are the Suns truly innocent?

378
00:21:32,279 --> 00:21:33,920
I came to ask for military funding

379
00:21:34,640 --> 00:21:36,160
and consolidate control over

380
00:21:36,279 --> 00:21:37,319
officials and merchants.

381
00:21:37,999 --> 00:21:38,640
I can't

382
00:21:39,239 --> 00:21:40,279
confront the Sun family

383
00:21:40,360 --> 00:21:40,999
just yet.

384
00:21:42,890 --> 00:21:44,810
(Great Virtue)

385
00:21:57,799 --> 00:21:58,319
Don't move.

386
00:22:09,890 --> 00:22:15,978
♪Constant yearning,
still vivid as our first meeting♪

387
00:22:17,008 --> 00:22:20,680
♪Endless gazing.
Step by step, falling deeper♪

388
00:22:20,680 --> 00:22:21,319
Does it hurt?

389
00:22:22,880 --> 00:22:23,408
No.

390
00:22:23,600 --> 00:22:24,239
I'm used to it.

391
00:22:27,039 --> 00:22:28,239
Just hand me the cup.

392
00:22:32,671 --> 00:22:37,986
♪My heart, unyielding as stone,
remains true♪

393
00:22:38,884 --> 00:22:42,704
♪Awaiting the crescent moon's
reflection in your heart♪

394
00:22:42,992 --> 00:22:46,000
♪Splendor fades from your eyes♪

395
00:22:46,960 --> 00:22:47,519
Have it.

396
00:22:50,239 --> 00:22:50,799
Not thirsty?

397
00:22:53,388 --> 00:22:57,488
♪Time lingers as you and I share
overlapping palm lines♪

398
00:22:57,488 --> 00:23:01,008
