400
00:23:16,360 --> 00:23:16,880
Are you cold?

401
00:23:19,559 --> 00:23:20,120
Not really.

402
00:23:21,079 --> 00:23:21,920
It's just that

403
00:23:22,279 --> 00:23:23,680
you're suddenly so nice to me.

404
00:23:24,079 --> 00:23:25,360
It's giving me goosebumps.

405
00:23:27,344 --> 00:23:33,066
♪Shadows hustle. Scenes reappear♪

406
00:23:34,519 --> 00:23:35,079
I'll...

407
00:23:36,719 --> 00:23:37,600
I'll go lie down.

408
00:23:42,640 --> 00:23:47,160
♪Through endless dawns and dusks,
to eternity♪

