423
00:24:51,279 --> 00:24:51,799
Rest now.

424
00:24:52,559 --> 00:24:53,400
I'll be right here

425
00:24:53,880 --> 00:24:54,519
for you.

426
00:25:05,319 --> 00:25:06,479
As you said, Commander,

427
00:25:06,960 --> 00:25:08,519
the assassination must be linked

428
00:25:08,640 --> 00:25:09,479
to Sun Xiangfu.

429
00:25:10,079 --> 00:25:11,120
And the servant was

430
00:25:11,319 --> 00:25:12,120
highly suspicious.

431
00:25:12,960 --> 00:25:13,488
That's right.

432
00:25:14,200 --> 00:25:15,039
This is our chance

433
00:25:15,160 --> 00:25:16,120
to infiltrate them

434
00:25:16,840 --> 00:25:17,519
and get to

435
00:25:18,640 --> 00:25:20,279
the bottom of everything.

436
00:25:21,039 --> 00:25:22,759
I discovered a hidden chamber here

437
00:25:23,200 --> 00:25:24,120
last time.

438
00:25:24,759 --> 00:25:25,680
The tax ledger

439
00:25:25,719 --> 00:25:26,719
is likely hidden there.

440
00:25:27,479 --> 00:25:28,360
But I was in a rush

441
00:25:28,519 --> 00:25:29,400
and the chamber was

442
00:25:30,559 --> 00:25:31,440
heavily guarded, so...

443
00:25:31,799 --> 00:25:32,360
It's fine.

444
00:25:32,999 --> 00:25:34,120
Since we are living here,

445
00:25:34,960 --> 00:25:36,039
we'll find a chance.

446
00:25:37,440 --> 00:25:38,400
But He Yan

447
00:25:39,200 --> 00:25:40,360
was implicated.

448
00:26:09,079 --> 00:26:11,360
(Xiao Jue is even more of a trouble
than I imagined,)

449
00:26:12,079 --> 00:26:13,400
(closing in step by step.)

450
00:26:14,960 --> 00:26:16,840
(We must hide the tax ledger well.)

451
00:26:18,093 --> 00:26:18,640
(Tax Ledger)

452
00:26:18,640 --> 00:26:19,920
(If Xiao Jue figures out)

453
00:26:19,999 --> 00:26:21,519
(that the tax records)

454
00:26:21,519 --> 00:26:22,559
(are falsified,)

455
00:26:22,719 --> 00:26:24,279
(we're finished.)

456
00:26:41,424 --> 00:26:42,607
(Account Book)

457
00:26:43,120 --> 00:26:45,400
(My life depends on this.)

458
00:26:57,120 --> 00:26:58,719
(As long as I hold on to this,)

459
00:26:59,120 --> 00:27:00,560
(Mr. Xu won't let anything)

460
00:27:00,560 --> 00:27:01,680
(happen to me.)

461
00:27:03,039 --> 00:27:03,799
(Otherwise,)

462
00:27:05,039 --> 00:27:06,640
(I'll drag him down with me.)

463
00:27:14,279 --> 00:27:15,880
(How dare Chu Zhao)

464
00:27:15,960 --> 00:27:18,719
(boss me around, acting arrogantly?)

465
00:27:18,840 --> 00:27:20,440
(I must remind him.)

466
00:27:21,799 --> 00:27:22,840
That he himself

467
00:27:23,920 --> 00:27:26,360
is merely another one of Mr. Xu's

468
00:27:27,519 --> 00:27:29,160
lackeys.

469
00:27:39,840 --> 00:27:41,440
Have some porridge.

470
00:27:48,200 --> 00:27:48,920
Thank you, Uncle.

471
00:27:49,440 --> 00:27:50,279
You've worked hard.

472
00:27:51,239 --> 00:27:52,279
I don't mind taking care

473
00:27:53,120 --> 00:27:53,719
of my nephew.

474
00:27:54,799 --> 00:27:56,120
Then could you please

475
00:27:56,360 --> 00:27:57,400
get me some side dishes

476
00:27:57,559 --> 00:27:58,479
for the porridge?

477
00:28:04,079 --> 00:28:04,880
And perhaps some

478
00:28:05,680 --> 00:28:06,559
family discipline.

479
00:28:07,920 --> 00:28:08,440
Open up.

480
00:28:11,600 --> 00:28:12,120
Commander.

481
00:28:12,960 --> 00:28:13,479
Mr. Cheng.

482
00:28:14,288 --> 00:28:14,920
This is

483
00:28:15,120 --> 00:28:15,799
our most famous

484
00:28:15,799 --> 00:28:16,680
and best oculist

485
00:28:16,960 --> 00:28:17,999
in Yezhou.

486
00:28:21,160 --> 00:28:22,479
Physician, you're finally here.

487
00:28:23,160 --> 00:28:24,239
This morning,

488
00:28:24,360 --> 00:28:26,039
I had cassia seeds

489
00:28:26,120 --> 00:28:27,039
with white peony root.

490
00:28:27,319 --> 00:28:28,360
I feel much better now.

491
00:28:28,600 --> 00:28:29,400
Please examine me.

492
00:28:29,799 --> 00:28:30,360
Good.

493
00:28:30,999 --> 00:28:32,880
Cassia seeds do improve vision.

494
00:28:33,680 --> 00:28:34,239
But still,

495
00:28:34,400 --> 00:28:35,279
let me

496
00:28:35,640 --> 00:28:37,440
examine you properly.

497
00:29:21,759 --> 00:29:22,559
(She can see?)

498
00:29:28,600 --> 00:29:29,160
Physician.

499
00:29:29,960 --> 00:29:31,160
We're both physicians.

500
00:29:31,640 --> 00:29:34,039
While cassia seeds improve vision,

501
00:29:34,479 --> 00:29:35,840
combining with white peony roots

502
00:29:36,120 --> 00:29:37,479
causes abdominal discomfort.

503
00:29:40,600 --> 00:29:41,759
As a physician,

504
00:29:42,200 --> 00:29:43,640
surely you know this?

505
00:29:48,759 --> 00:29:50,160
You're right, Mr. Cheng.

506
00:29:50,600 --> 00:29:51,200
I am

507
00:29:51,559 --> 00:29:52,519
getting senile

508
00:29:52,799 --> 00:29:53,519
and confused.

509
00:29:54,279 --> 00:29:55,759
I almost made a grave mistake.

510
00:29:56,479 --> 00:29:57,079
It's alright.

511
00:29:57,519 --> 00:29:58,880
Just prescribe me something

512
00:29:58,960 --> 00:29:59,999
more effective.

513
00:30:01,039 --> 00:30:01,719
But

514
00:30:01,719 --> 00:30:02,719
make it less bitter.

515
00:30:05,279 --> 00:30:06,120
Do as he says.

516
00:30:06,559 --> 00:30:07,799
Alright.

517
00:30:26,920 --> 00:30:28,200
(That powder was strong.)

518
00:30:29,079 --> 00:30:30,120
(I did lose my vision)

519
00:30:30,519 --> 00:30:31,680
(when it got into my eyes.)

520
00:30:33,120 --> 00:30:33,880
(Without the drug)

521
00:30:33,880 --> 00:30:34,759
(Master left me,)

522
00:30:35,400 --> 00:30:36,719
(I'd be blind again.)

523
00:30:38,479 --> 00:30:39,840
(Since they think I'm blind,)

524
00:30:40,600 --> 00:30:41,799
(I'll play along)

525
00:30:42,519 --> 00:30:43,759
(to lower their guard)

526
00:30:44,440 --> 00:30:45,759
(for our plan.)

527
00:30:47,440 --> 00:30:48,200
(After all,)

528
00:30:49,120 --> 00:30:50,840
(nobody guards against a blind person.)

529
00:31:11,719 --> 00:31:12,759
(Let's see how long)

530
00:31:13,960 --> 00:31:15,120
(you'll keep this act.)

531
00:31:19,600 --> 00:31:20,160
(Did he)

532
00:31:20,719 --> 00:31:22,440
(notice something?)

533
00:31:30,200 --> 00:31:31,319
Brewing medicine takes time.

534
00:31:31,799 --> 00:31:32,519
Go get some air.

535
00:31:35,479 --> 00:31:36,079
Alright.

536
00:31:39,600 --> 00:31:40,559
Proxy kill was my plan.

537
00:31:41,039 --> 00:31:42,200
Too bad the proxy's an idiot.

538
00:31:43,079 --> 00:31:44,120
Now the enemy is alerted.

539
00:31:44,440 --> 00:31:45,200
Time's running out.

540
00:31:45,680 --> 00:31:47,239
Locate the hidden ledger of Sun Xiangfu

541
00:31:47,600 --> 00:31:49,039
and Master's dealings quickly.

542
00:31:49,744 --> 00:31:50,352
Understood.

543
00:31:52,840 --> 00:31:53,440
Mind the step.

544
00:31:58,090 --> 00:31:59,600
(Peace and Prosperity)

545
00:32:12,079 --> 00:32:13,200
It hurts!

546
00:32:18,200 --> 00:32:20,120
Commander's waist is indeed slender.

547
00:32:22,559 --> 00:32:23,440
That's enough.

548
00:32:27,440 --> 00:32:27,960
Uncle.

549
00:32:28,079 --> 00:32:29,319
Where are we going?

550
00:32:30,519 --> 00:32:31,680
Would I abandon you?

551
00:32:32,680 --> 00:32:33,600
Just follow me.

552
00:32:58,120 --> 00:32:58,640
Uncle?

553
00:32:59,960 --> 00:33:00,640
Uncle.

554
00:33:02,519 --> 00:33:03,200
Uncle!

555
00:33:07,319 --> 00:33:08,600
Unbelievable!

556
00:33:08,880 --> 00:33:10,239
He actually left me alone.

557
00:33:18,999 --> 00:33:20,239
Hey! Someone!

558
00:33:20,440 --> 00:33:21,759
I can't see.

559
00:33:22,200 --> 00:33:23,640
I'm blind. I'm lost.

560
00:33:23,640 --> 00:33:24,400
Hey! Help!

561
00:33:24,519 --> 00:33:25,400
Where am I?

562
00:33:26,440 --> 00:33:27,559
What is this place?

563
00:33:27,719 --> 00:33:28,400
No entry here.

564
00:33:28,479 --> 00:33:29,039
W-Who are you?

565
00:33:29,039 --> 00:33:29,640
Go back now.

566
00:33:30,079 --> 00:33:31,160
Why are you pulling me?

567
00:33:31,719 --> 00:33:32,640
Do you know who I am?

568
00:33:32,680 --> 00:33:33,719
Why are you pulling me?

569
00:33:33,759 --> 00:33:34,519
Let go.

570
00:33:35,999 --> 00:33:37,279
Stop pulling me.

571
00:33:37,640 --> 00:33:39,840
I'm blind. You're bullying me.

572
00:33:41,239 --> 00:33:42,479
I'm lost.

573
00:33:43,759 --> 00:33:45,279
Take me back, will you?

574
00:33:46,519 --> 00:33:48,120
Find my uncle.

575
00:34:09,920 --> 00:34:11,319
(The top part's way smoother)

576
00:34:11,319 --> 00:34:12,160
(than the rest.)

577
00:34:13,159 --> 00:34:15,240
(Someone touches it very often.)

578
00:35:35,880 --> 00:35:37,320
Let go. I can walk.

579
00:35:37,479 --> 00:35:37,999
Young Master.

580
00:35:38,280 --> 00:35:38,880
Get lost.

581
00:35:39,800 --> 00:35:40,559
Why should I

582
00:35:40,639 --> 00:35:41,440
visit Xiao Jue?

583
00:35:41,760 --> 00:35:42,599
I'm not going.

584
00:35:42,999 --> 00:35:44,280
I'd rather go to sleep.

585
00:35:45,320 --> 00:35:45,679
(Oh no.)

586
00:35:45,880 --> 00:35:46,639
(Sun Ling is back.)

587
00:35:51,280 --> 00:35:52,800
(The mechanism is so complex.)

588
00:35:53,599 --> 00:35:54,840
(It only opens if I pull)

589
00:35:54,999 --> 00:35:56,079
(the copper strips)

590
00:35:56,119 --> 00:35:56,960
(in the right order.)

591
00:35:57,720 --> 00:35:58,720
